trainings.name: Full Body Strength Training
trainings.description: A comprehensive workout to build strength and muscle mass.

exercises.title: Barbell Squats
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet shoulder-width apart, lower the bar onto your upper back, and squat down until your thighs are parallel to the ground.

exercises.title: Push-Ups
exercises.instructions: Place hands shoulder-width apart, lower your chest towards the floor, and push back up.

exercises.title: Pull-Ups
exercises.instructions: Grab a pull-up bar with an overhand grip, hang with arms fully extended, and pull yourself up until your chin is over the bar.

exercises.title: Dumbbell Rows
exercises.instructions: Hinge at your hips, keep your back straight, and pull the dumbbells towards your chest.

exercises.title: Overhead Press
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet shoulder-width apart, hold dumbbells at shoulder height, and press them straight up overhead.

trainings.name: Yoga for Flexibility
trainings.description: Improve your flexibility and range of motion with this yoga flow.

exercises.title: Downward Dog
exercises.instructions: Start on all fours, lift your hips up and back, forming an inverted V-shape with your body.

exercises.title: Warrior II Pose
exercises.instructions: Step your feet wide apart, turn your right foot out, and bend your right knee.

exercises.title: Triangle Pose
exercises.instructions: From Warrior II, straighten your right leg and reach your right hand forward.

exercises.title: Pigeon Pose
exercises.instructions: Bring your right shin forward and your left leg back, resting on your hips.

exercises.title: Child's Pose
exercises.instructions: Kneel on the floor, bring your big toes together, and rest your forehead on the ground.
